        <section id="dev">
            <title>Developing eXist-db</title>
    

    <p>The following articles provide information on how to work on eXist-db itself, either by enhancing its code or providing documentation.</p>

    <dl>
                <dlentry>
                    <dt>
          <xref href="devguide_manifesto" scope="external">eXist-db Developer Manifesto</xref>
        </dt>
                    <dd>
          <p>Guidelines for developers who wish to contribute to eXist-db's code base.</p>
        </dd>
                </dlentry>
                <dlentry>
                    <dt>
          <xref href="devguide_codereview" scope="external">Code Review Guide</xref>
        </dt>
                    <dd>
          <p>How to review somebody else's (or your own of course) code.</p>
        </dd>
                </dlentry>
                <dlentry>
